#- The Goat's New Home










-A Children's Tale
By NukeJay
#- The goat stood infront
of the house, the
beaver had been kind
enough to build for
said goat.
"This is just a crappy 
pile of wood, yo
suck!" said the goat
and tore down the 
house.

The End.
#- 